**Baroness Spying** | Attribute
__Basics__
An attribute marking all players that a baroness is currently spying on.

__Formalized__
Starting: Target @ThisAttr->Source (Player) {Visitless}

On Any Action [Investigating]: Reveal `@Self->Role information @ActionFeedback` to @Target [Condition: @TriggerSource is part of `Role:Fortune Teller`+`Role:Huntsman`+`Role:Innkeeper`+`Role:Clairvoyant Fox`+`Role:Lone Warlock`+`Role:Warlock`+`Role:Flute Charmer`]

On Any Action [Feedback]: Reveal `@Self->Role information @ActionFeedback` to @Target [Condition: @TriggerSource is part of `Role:Crowd Seeker`+`Role:Aura Teller`+`Role:Tracking Wolf`+`Role:Psychic Wolf`+`Role:Oracle`]
